Device/ParallelPort/drv/parport
===============================

This is a Device::ParallelPort driver that uses direct IO access on linux. It
uses the linux parport driver and is definitely the prefered access method on
linux. It also means that you do not require root access.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Device::ParallelPort

